<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1436,1303,1471]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
Geographical distribution: 
<collectingCountry box="[501,612,1340,1364]" name="Colombia" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Colombia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[667,739,1340,1364]" name="Brazil" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Perez-Goodwyn" box="[750,1014,1340,1364]" firstAuthor="Perez-Goodwyn" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" pagination="1 - 71" refId="ref41737" refString="Perez-Goodwyn, P. J. (2006) Taxonomic revision of the subfamily Lethocerinae Lauck &amp; Menke (Heteroptera: Belostomatidae). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A (Biologie), 695, 1 - 71." type="journal article" year="2006">Perez-Goodwyn (2006)</bibRefCitation>
restricted the distribution of this species to 
<collectingCountry box="[230,343,1375,1399]" name="Colombia" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, and Southeastern and Southern 
<collectingCountry box="[709,781,1375,1399]" name="Brazil" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. Records from outside this area are not considered here.
</paragraph>
